Twemoji Spiral Shell
--------------------

ClamshellCtl uses the Twemoji Spiral Shell artwork for its GUI icon.

Source: https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Twemoji_1f41a.svg
Original project: https://github.com/twitter/twemoji
Copyright: 2019 Twitter, Inc and other contributors
License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
License URL: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

The icon is bundled as SVG, PNG, and ICNS assets. The PNG and ICNS files are
rendered from the SVG for macOS app packaging.
